This paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category as it deals with image classification and label prediction. The use of deep learning frameworks also suggests that it could belong to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also mentions the use of label graphs, which could indicate that it belongs to the artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses the capture of intra-level label semantics, which could suggest that it belongs to the natural language processing (cs.CL) sub-category. Finally, the evaluation of the proposed method on benchmark image datasets could indicate that it belongs to the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
